folder: Henry Hudson Parkway & 227th Street (West), Bronx, NY
text:
(1)
Henry Hudson Parkway (Spuyten Duyvil Parkway), west side, north from West 227th (left) to 230th Streets, showing a comprehensive view of part of the Spuyten Duyvil section of the borough. In the left background appears the Henry Hudson Monument.

About 1936.


(2)
An exclusive view of the Henry Hudson Monument as seen from Independence Ave.
May 25, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.
